qlibxmlnodemodel - A QAbstractXmlNodeModel for using with libxml2 library
=========================================================================

QLibXmlNodeModel obviously depends on Qt, version 4.6 or higher. If
you're on *nix (Linux, BSD, Mac OS X ...), install libxml2 and run

$ mkdir build && cd build
$ cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/path/to/installation/prefix
$ make
$ make install

To create debug build pass to cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug option. This is a
standard cmake option, see the cmake man page for details.
